@host = https://localhost:5103

### 1) Cookie login (oturum ac — sonraki istekler Cookies header'i otomatik kullanir)
POST {{host}}/Account/Login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=admin@calibra.local&password=12345678

### 2) Metadata: mevcut VIEW'lari listele
GET {{host}}/api/reporting/views

### 3) VIEW detay (kolonlar + roller)
GET {{host}}/api/reporting/views/1

### 4) INFORMATION_SCHEMA kesif — RptViewCol'a eklenmemis kolonlari gosterir
GET {{host}}/api/reporting/views/1/discover-columns

### 5) Ad-hoc execute — duz tablo
POST {{host}}/api/reporting/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "viewId": 1,
  "adHocConfigJson": "{\"category\":1,\"columns\":[{\"colName\":\"id\"},{\"colName\":\"doc_no\"},{\"colName\":\"doc_date\"}],\"orderBy\":[{\"colName\":\"doc_date\",\"descending\":true}],\"topN\":50,\"injectContext\":false}",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 50
}

### 6) Ad-hoc execute — grupli chart (ornek)
POST {{host}}/api/reporting/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "viewId": 1,
  "adHocConfigJson": "{\"category\":2,\"groupBy\":[{\"colName\":\"doc_date\"}],\"aggregates\":[{\"colName\":\"grand_total\",\"fn\":3,\"alias\":\"Toplam\"}],\"chart\":{\"type\":\"bar\",\"xColumn\":\"doc_date\",\"yColumns\":[\"Toplam\"]},\"orderBy\":[{\"colName\":\"doc_date\",\"descending\":false}],\"injectContext\":false}",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 100
}

### 7) CSV export (ExportReports izni gerekir)
POST {{host}}/api/reporting/execute/csv
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "viewId": 1,
  "adHocConfigJson": "{\"category\":1,\"columns\":[{\"colName\":\"id\"},{\"colName\":\"doc_no\"}],\"topN\":500,\"injectContext\":false}"
}

### 8) Negatif: olmayan kolon — 400 dondurmeli
POST {{host}}/api/reporting/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "viewId": 1,
  "adHocConfigJson": "{\"category\":1,\"columns\":[{\"colName\":\"1=1; DROP TABLE RptDef --\"}]}"
}

### 9) Negatif: gecersiz operator — 400 dondurmeli
POST {{host}}/api/reporting/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "viewId": 1,
  "adHocConfigJson": "{\"category\":1,\"columns\":[{\"colName\":\"id\"}],\"filters\":[{\"colName\":\"id\",\"op\":999,\"values\":[1]}]}"
}

### 10) Admin: VIEW upsert (ManageReports izni gerekir)
PUT {{host}}/api/reporting/admin/views
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "code": "DEMO_SALES",
  "name": "Demo Satis",
  "sqlObjectName": "vw_DemoSales",
  "description": "Ornek",
  "isActive": true
}

### 11) Rapor tanimi listele
GET {{host}}/api/reporting/definitions

### 12) Rapor tanimi kaydet (DesignReports izni gerekir)
PUT {{host}}/api/reporting/definitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "code": "SALES_TREND",
  "name": "Aylik Ciro Trendi",
  "viewId": 1,
  "category": 2,
  "configJson": "{\"category\":2,\"groupBy\":[{\"colName\":\"doc_date\"}],\"aggregates\":[{\"colName\":\"grand_total\",\"fn\":3,\"alias\":\"Toplam\"}],\"chart\":{\"type\":\"line\",\"xColumn\":\"doc_date\",\"yColumns\":[\"Toplam\"]},\"injectContext\":false}",
  "isShared": false,
  "roles": []
}
